  block t_mrwb: TextBlock {
    content: @md ## Emergency Flow Inefficiency

L4–L5 non-urgent cases dominate, driving inefficiency. Wait times peak in early mornings despite lower volume, suggesting staffing misalignment.;;
    theme {
      label {
        font_color: '1a1a2e'
      }
      text {
        font_color: '#4A4A6A'
      }
      border {
        border_width: 0
        border_radius: 12
      }
      background {
        bg_color: 'transparent'
      }
    }
  }
